data.description: Almost new brick and stone home built in 2018. 2 story home on a quiet, end of street, cul-de-sac 4 BED 3 BATH PLUS downstairs powder room. Primary bedroom on first floor. Easy access to 410 and 1604. Nice spacious kitchen open to living. New appliances. Lots of light. Game room and Media room. Nice backyard with covered porch. Close to all the shopping, restaurants, medical and located in Northside School District. Ready to move in! Easy to show.
